    <item>
      <title>必和必拓审查镍资产以缓解价格大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bhp-s-quarterly-iron-ore-production-dips-2-copper-edges-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司正在考虑其澳大利亚镍业务的选择，以减轻价格大幅下跌的影响，并警告称，该公司可能被迫减记资产价值，这是绿色金属行业遇到麻烦的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bhp-s-quarterly-iron-ore-production-dips-2-copper-edges-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 21:36:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国将在提高塔卡利率的同时引入爬行挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行表示，正在考虑引入爬行钉住汇率制度以保持本国货币稳定，同时提高了关键利率并缩小了利率走廊以应对顽固的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
